點樣拎新花結<br />\nA:做完集會新七星任-大連續(雌火&amp;轟龍&amp;妃蜘蛛)寒冷群島金獅子捕獲任務,就有<br />\n<br />\nQ:邊到刷護石料<br />\nA:自己開雷神/爆鱗團<br />\n<br />\nQ:邊到刷新原珠<br />\nA:各大單獨首領任務"},{"pid":"1dca5ef0be712eceeed9411cceacae264bf0688f","tid":2513639,"uid":58266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T16:17:56.000Z","msg":"玩爛左徹甲啦，有無近戰團？"},{"pid":"c7045e4362b6f9cf83334b1a3194aed3655ff0d8","tid":2513639,"uid":43016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1dca5ef0be712eceeed9411cceacae264bf0688f","tid":2513639,"uid":58266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T16:17:56.000Z","msg":"玩爛左徹甲啦，有無近戰團？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T16:18:41.000Z","msg":"我今晚開完了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"113eba8ca434d389af427a583a94fdf67b5bc2ac","tid":2513639,"uid":148449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T16:19:03.000Z","msg":"自己去打轟龍啲料 比佢連環撞死2次<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de8f57adc2690c058edf53e45d402eaf4aa8e93f","tid":2513639,"uid":30694,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T16:19:08.000Z","msg":"垃圾1001"},{"pid":"daf6e02da79416ec8ecc164d42e667d905b77e0c","tid":2513639,"uid":51948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T16:19:49.000Z","msg":"呢版力解仲有冇人會用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n啱啱出左粒力解3  2-1 放落弓到好似唔差"},{"pid":"cb2f31f2412a0271a179045334956679c2a27b78","tid":2513639,"uid":58266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7045e4362b6f9cf83334b1a3194aed3655ff0d8","tid":2513639,"uid":43016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1dca5ef0be712eceeed9411cceacae264bf0688f","tid":2513639,"uid":58266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T16:17:56.000Z","msg":"玩爛左徹甲啦，有無近戰團？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T16:18:41.000Z","msg":"我今晚開完了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"re